:{{DIcon|Talk}} Why do you want to protect the rights and interests of non-human creatures?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011122-->
::'''Lukacs:''' Good question! Only by understanding the motives behind the actions can mutual understanding be truly achieved.
::'''Lukacs:''' Among the countless Curio collections of the space station, life does not only exist in the human receptacle.
::'''Lukacs:''' They often inhabit places that humans can't imagine &mdash; such as a table or a cup.
::'''Lukacs:''' However, just because their appearances are not understood by humans, their lives are not valued!
::'''Lukacs:''' How ridiculous? How can anyone segregate life into different levels just because of their external forms?
::'''Lukacs:''' For this very reason, I decided to establish the Mimicry Protection Association to protect the rights and interests of non-human creatures.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} What have you done as the president of the Mimicry Protection Association?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011129-->
::'''Lukacs:''' I am powerless on my own. My influence may disappoint you.
::'''Lukacs:''' But I swear on my soul that I never treated this matter with any less importance. Every day, I work hard to promote the Mimicry Protection Association!
::'''Lukacs:''' Other than recruiting like-minded people like now, I also compiled the ''Robot Slavery Abolition Act''. Although it is only a draft, I've got the preliminary framework set up.
::'''Lukacs:''' Have some faith in the future. I'm sure we can change this cold-blooded status quo!
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} What are the other people's perspectives on your actions?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011134-->
::'''Lukacs:''' Unfortunately, most of the researchers here are selfish. They care too much about short-term interests. They are more willing to put their efforts into things like promotion and salary.
::'''Lukacs:''' I'll be honest with you. They think my idea is premature and unrealistic.
::'''Lukacs:''' But fortunately, once in a while I meet people like you who share the ambition. It gives me faith to stick to the right path.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have any other questions.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011138-->
::'''Lukacs:''' Although we didn't chat long, I can feel that you already understood everything I try to express.
::'''Lukacs:''' I hope we can make more efforts in protecting the rights and interests of non-human creatures in the future!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
