::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 90000007: Config/Level/NPC/W0/NPC_DefaultStory_500001101.json-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_500011102-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011102-->
::'''Lukacs:''' Raise your proud heads! Don't try to deceive yourself by ignoring the tragedies right in front of your eyes!
::'''Lukacs:''' Have you ever thought about the feeling of the robot arm when you order a cup of latte that requires 1,000 wisks?
::'''Lukacs:''' Did it ever occur to you that the non-human Curios can also feel pain when you cast excessive external stimulation to it just to see its unique response?
::'''Lukacs:''' Emotion is not exclusive to humans. Facing the tragedy of non-human creatures around you is the first step to truly understand love!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_500010114_707-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_500010114_707-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How can you protect the rights and interests of non-human creatures?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011107-->
:::'''Lukacs:''' Oh, great! After yelling and shouting for a whole day, there's finally someone who understands me!
:::'''Lukacs:''' My brethern, my compatriot, please allow me to introduce myself.
:::'''Lukacs:''' My name is Lukacs. I am currently the president of the Mimicry Protection Association and a researcher at the Department of Galactic Geopolitics.
:::'''Lukacs:''' The protection of non-human creatures' rights and interests is a rather macro topic. If you are in a hurry, I can only give you a brief introduction.
:::'''Lukacs:''' Let's start from the most simple aspect &mdash; the last Legion invasion. People were desperate to escape but no one cared about the safety of the Curios!
:::'''Lukacs:''' This is the space station's current situation. It's also a representation that the non-human creatures' rights are not protected!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How can we alleviate the enslavement of robots?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011114-->
:::'''Lukacs:''' You hit the nail on the head, my friend.
:::'''Lukacs:''' I can see you have sharp eyes and you are good at spotting the most essential pain point of the issue.
:::'''Lukacs:''' I'm sure everyone can see the level of science and technology in the space station. However, people show no respect for machines.
:::'''Lukacs:''' People get rid of them when broken, and replace them when they start to slow down. It's a very dangerous mindset.
:::'''Lukacs:''' This is the current situation! It is very bad!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_500010114_722-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_500010114_722-->
;(Subsequent interactions)
